<h2>Spellcasting and Prayers</h2>
<p>To Cast a Spell the Spellcaster must use an action, choose a spell and roll 2D6, if it equals to or beast the difficulty of the spell it is cast and its effects go off as normal.</p>
<p>Each spellcaster can only cast a single spell in a turn, and may not use missile weapons and cast a spell in the same activation, </p>
<p>Spellcasters can not wear armour and cast spells, Prayer users can wear armour and still use Prayers</p>
<p>More details are listed on the Spells/Prayers page</p>
